overview: Your Words Make No Sense To Me, You Speak Them In Vain, Your Eyes Look Upon Me, Yet You Ignore My Present Pain. I Despise Your Reluctant Helping Hand, I Don’t Need You To Love Me, I Don’t Want You To Understand. Have You Or Have You Not. Will You Or Will You Not. Can You Or Can You Not. Are You Or Are You Not. Am I Who You Think You Are?
title: Seen From Outside Creation
